trans-unit.source: Represents a dialog box that allows the user to choose a type.
trans-unit.target: Représente une boîte de dialogue qui permet à l'utilisateur de choisir un type.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Cette classe ne peut pas être héritée.

trans-unit.source: This class prompts the user to browse a list of Windows Workflow Foundation and .NET Framework namespaces and their contained types and select a single type.
trans-unit.target: Cette classe invite l'utilisateur à parcourir une liste d'espaces de noms Windows Workflow Foundation et .NET Framework et leurs types contenus, et à sélectionner un type unique.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialise une nouvelle instance de la classe <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.IServiceProvider" /> from which the dialog obtains services.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.IServiceProvider" /> à partir duquel la boîte de dialogue obtient des services.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ITypeFilterProvider" /> from which to obtain type filtering services.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ITypeFilterProvider" /> à partir duquel obtenir des services de filtrage de type.

trans-unit.source: The name of the selected type.
trans-unit.target: Nom du type sélectionné.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog" /> class by using an <see cref="T:System.IServiceProvider" />, an <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ITypeFilterProvider" />, and a string.
trans-unit.target: Initialise une nouvelle instance de la classe <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog" /> en utilisant <see cref="T:System.IServiceProvider" />, <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ITypeFilterProvider" /> et une chaîne.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.IServiceProvider" /> from which to obtain services.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.IServiceProvider" /> à partir duquel obtenir des services.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ITypeFilterProvider" /> from which to obtain type filtering services.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ITypeFilterProvider" /> à partir duquel obtenir des services de filtrage de type.

trans-unit.source: The name of the selected type.
trans-unit.target: Nom du type sélectionné.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.TypeProvider" /> that allows access local assemblies to load in the type browser dialog.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.TypeProvider" /> qui autorise le chargement des assemblys d'accès locaux dans la boîte de dialogue de recherche de type.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog" /> class by using an <see cref="T:System.IServiceProvider" />, an <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ITypeFilterProvider" />, a string, and a <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.TypeProvider" />.
trans-unit.target: Initialise une nouvelle instance de la classe <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog" /> en utilisant un <see cref="T:System.IServiceProvider" />, un <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ITypeFilterProvider" />, une chaîne et un <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.TypeProvider" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the type selected by the user in the type browser dialog box.
trans-unit.target: Obtient le type sélectionné par l'utilisateur dans la boîte de dialogue de recherche de type.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Type" /> selected by the user in the type browser dialog box.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Type" /> sélectionné par l'utilisateur dans la boîte de dialogue de recherche de type.

trans-unit.source: Gets the component to associate with the type browser dialog box.
trans-unit.target: Obtient le composant à associer à la boîte de dialogue de recherche de type.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.IComponent" /> to bind to the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.IComponent" /> à lier au <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog" />.

trans-unit.source: If the property returns a valid value--anything other than a null reference (`Nothing` in Visual Basic)--the component is added to <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>.
trans-unit.target: Si la propriété retourne une valeur valide, c'est-à-dire une valeur autre qu'une référence Null (`Nothing` en Visual Basic), le composant est ajouté à <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>.

trans-unit.source: This property is required because <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog> implements <xref:System.ComponentModel.ISite>.
trans-unit.target: Cette propriété est requise car <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog> implémente <xref:System.ComponentModel.ISite>.

trans-unit.source: For <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System%23ComponentModel%23ISite%23Component?displayProperty=nameWithType> always returns a null reference (`Nothing` in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: Pour <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System%23ComponentModel%23ISite%23Component?displayProperty=nameWithType> retourne toujours une référence null (`Nothing` en Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: Gets the container to associate with the type browser dialog.
trans-unit.target: Obtient le conteneur à associer à la boîte de dialogue de recherche de type.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.IContainer" /> to associate with the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.IContainer" /> à associer à <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog" />.

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System%23ComponentModel%23ISite%23Container> returns a null reference (`Nothing` in Visual Basic), <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System%23ComponentModel%23ISite%23Component> has not bound an <xref:System.ComponentModel.IComponent> to the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>.
trans-unit.target: Si <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System%23ComponentModel%23ISite%23Container> retourne une référence null (`Nothing` en Visual Basic), <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System%23ComponentModel%23ISite%23Component> n'a pas lié de <xref:System.ComponentModel.IComponent> au <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>.

trans-unit.source: This method is required because <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog> implements <xref:System.ComponentModel.ISite>.
trans-unit.target: Cette méthode est requise car <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog> implémente <xref:System.ComponentModel.ISite>.

trans-unit.source: For <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System%23ComponentModel%23ISite%23Container?displayProperty=nameWithType> always returns a null reference (`Nothing` in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: Pour <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System%23ComponentModel%23ISite%23Container?displayProperty=nameWithType> retourne toujours une référence null (`Nothing` en Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the type browser dialog is in design mode.
trans-unit.target: Obtient une valeur qui indique si la boîte de dialogue de recherche de type est en mode Création.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog" /> is in design mode; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> si <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog" /> est en mode Création ; sinon, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: The default is <see langword="true" />.
trans-unit.target: La valeur par défaut est <see langword="true" />.

trans-unit.source: This property is required because <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog> implements <xref:System.ComponentModel.ISite>.
trans-unit.target: Cette propriété est requise car <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog> implémente <xref:System.ComponentModel.ISite>.

trans-unit.source: For <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System%23ComponentModel%23ISite%23DesignMode%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> always returns `true`.
trans-unit.target: Pour <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System%23ComponentModel%23ISite%23DesignMode%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> retourne toujours `true`.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets name of the component associated with the type browser dialog.
trans-unit.target: Obtient ou définit le nom du composant associé à la boîte de dialogue de recherche de type.

trans-unit.source: The name of the component associated with the type browser dialog.
trans-unit.target: Nom du composant associé à la boîte de dialogue de recherche de type.

trans-unit.source: This property is required because <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog> implements <xref:System.ComponentModel.ISite>.
trans-unit.target: Cette propriété est requise car <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog> implémente <xref:System.ComponentModel.ISite>.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Type" /> of service object to retrieve.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Type" /> d'objet de service à récupérer.

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the service object for the specified type.
trans-unit.target: Récupère l'objet de service pour le type spécifié.

trans-unit.source: A service object of type <paramref name="serviceType" />, or a null reference (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic) if there is no service object of type <paramref name="serviceType" />.
trans-unit.target: Un objet de service de type <paramref name="serviceType" /> ou une référence Null (<see langword="Nothing" /> en Visual Basic) s'il n'y a aucun objet de service de type <paramref name="serviceType" />.

trans-unit.source: If `serviceType` is of type <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.ITypeProvider>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System%23IServiceProvider%23GetService%2A> returns a service object.
trans-unit.target: Si `serviceType` est de type <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.ITypeProvider>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System%23IServiceProvider%23GetService%2A> retourne un objet de service.

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, it returns a null reference (`Nothing` in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: Sinon, elle retourne une référence null (`Nothing` en Visual Basic).
